<P>A WEDDING Ring for the Finger; <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">e <HI>Salve</HI> of <HI>Divin<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="3 letters"></HI> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">he Sore of <HI>Humanity.</HI></P>
<P>Directions to tho<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> Wives, how to <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"> and <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span"></P>
