Wedding; Let none but th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">&s;e who have found fa|vour in Gods eyes, find favour in yours.</P>
<P N="2">2 Give God the Tribute of your gratulation for your good Companions. Take heed of paying your Rent to a wrong Landlord When you ta&s;te of the &s;tream, reflect on the Sting that feeds it. Now thou ha&s;t four eyes for thy &s;peculation, four hands
