womans is to pre&s;erve di&s;|creetly; the one mu&s;t not be carele&s;ly wanting, the other must not becau&s;le&s;ly wa&s;ting: the man mu&s;t be &s;eeking with diligence, the woman mu&s;t be &s;aving with providence. The Cock and the Hen both &s;crape together in the du&s;t <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">eap to pick up &s;omething for their little chickens</HI></P>
