<P><HI>Secundus</HI> being a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ked his opinion of a Woman, &s;peaks thus, <HI>Viri naufragi|um, domus tempe&s;tas, quie|tis impedimentum, &amp;c.</HI> But &s;urely he was a Mon|&s;ter, and not a man, fitte<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> for a Tomb to bury him, than a womb to bear <HI>him.</HI></P>
