<P><HI>It is not good to play the Butcher with that naked Sex that hath no arms but for imbraces. A Preacher &s;hould not be &s;ilent for tho&s;e who are &s;ilenced from preach+ing; becau&s;e they are the weaker Ve&s;&s;els, &s;hall they be broken all to pieces? Thou that &s;aye&s;t women are evil,
