<P N="2">2 <HI>Is the woman to be help to the man? Then let the man be a help to the wo|<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">. What makes the&s;e Debtors be &s;uch ill Pay-Ma|&s;ters&punc; but becau&s;e they look at what is owing to them, <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> not at what is owing by <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">. If thou woulde&s;t have <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> wives reverence, let her have thy re&s;pect. To force <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word">
